 "description": "Calls a dead character back — in another body. The new form follows the dead one's alignment: roll on the Character Alignment table, and whatever comes up, that creature the character now is, and so must play. Returned as a man, he rolls class and a six-sided die for level; likewise level is diced for return as an elf or dwarf.",
